{"tid":649353,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日同個青梅竹馬表白,佢拒絕左我","createTime":"2018-05-01T13:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T13:32:24.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9634ed074ba30ee937ee2cd03d42485ad2e85e7","tid":649353,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"我同佢由細玩到大,感情好好<br />\n幼稚園同小學都係讀同一間<br />\n細個時試過一齊沖涼,一齊訓<br />\n兩小冇猜,到左中學後大家就分開左讀書<br />\n佢漸漸疏遠左我,亦識左好多新朋友<br />\n開始唔多理我,我好妒忌<br />\n今日終於鼓起勇氣向佢表白<br />\n佢呆左呆,話對我唔係呢種感覺,冇feel...<br />\n我唔信,我地一齊左咁耐,我伸手摸佢下面<br />\n發現真係冇硬到,點摸佢都唔起<br />\n我好傷心咁走左出去,有冇人可以開解我"},{"pid":"67d41e12f05116f9830903a33a5f5aa5e0c5eae6","tid":649353,"uid":50744,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:23:23.000Z","msg":"太早開估<br />\n欠佈局<br />\n3.5/10"},{"pid":"af1a108c708c75de9ec80c89be96afabd2426127","tid":649353,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/213222_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F213222_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f9a1ecc6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}